                        },
                        {
                            "type": "p",
                            "content": "Controller: It serves as the application core. This is where the logic resides that connects the data with the interface."
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "p",
                            "content": "View: It represents the application's user interface. It includes forms, texts, buttons, and other related elements."
